@startuml Activity Diagram - Search and Filter Operations
!theme cerulean-outline

title SmartMedia - Search and Filter Activity Diagram

|User|
start

:Open HomePage;

|System|
:Load images from\nSQLite database;

:Display gallery grid;

|User|
fork
  -> Search by text;
  :Enter search query\nin search bar;
  
  |System|
  :Capture input;
  
  :Apply 300ms debounce;
  note right: Prevents excessive\nre-renders
  
  :Convert query to\nlowercase;
  
  partition "Text Matching" {
    :Search in image.caption;
    
    :Search in image.filename;
    
    :Search in image.tags[];
    
    :Search in image.objects[];
    
    :Combine all matches;
  }
  
  :Filter images array;
  
  :Update filteredImages state;
  
  :Re-render gallery;
  
  if (Results found?) then (Yes)
    :Display matching images;
  else (No)
    :Show "No results" message;
  endif

fork again
  -> Filter by tags;
  :Click tag filter button;
  
  |System|
  :Show all available tags;
  
  |User|
  repeat
    :Select tag;
    
    |System|
    :Add tag to selectedTags[];
    
    :Update tag chips display;
    
    partition "Tag Filtering" {
      if (Multiple tags selected?) then (Yes)
        :Apply AND logic;
        note right: Image must have\nALL selected tags
        
        repeat :Check image.tags[];
          if (Contains all selected tags?) then (Yes)
            :Include in results;
          else (No)
            :Exclude from results;
          endif
        repeat while (More images?) is (Yes)
      else (Single tag)
        :Match single tag;
      endif
    }
    
    :Update gallery display;
    
  repeat while (User selects more tags?) is (Yes)
  ->No;

fork again
  -> Navigate to Albums;
  :Click "Albums" in sidebar;
  
  |System|
  :Navigate to AlbumsPage;
  
  :Generate smart albums;
  
  partition "Smart Album Generation" {
    :Group by album_category;
    
    fork
      :Filter images where\nalbum_category = 'Selfies';
      :Create "Selfies" album;
    fork again
      :Filter images where\nalbum_category = 'Events';
      :Create "Events" album;
    fork again
      :Filter images where\nalbum_category = 'Documents';
      :Create "Documents" album;
    fork again
      :Filter images where\nalbum_category = 'Locations';
      :Create "Locations" album;
    fork again
      :Filter remaining images;
      :Create "Others" album;
    end fork
  }
  
  :Display album cards;
  
  |User|
  :Click album card;
  
  |System|
  :Filter images by\nselected album;
  
  :Display album contents;

fork again
  -> Filter by Emotions;
  :Click "Emotions" in sidebar;
  
  |System|
  :Navigate to EmotionsPage;
  
  partition "Emotion Aggregation" {
    :Scan all images;
    
    repeat :Read image.metadata.emotion;
      
      if (Emotion exists?) then (Yes)
        :Increment emotion counter;
      endif
      
    repeat while (More images?) is (Yes)
    ->No;
    
    :Sort emotions by count;
  }
  
  :Display emotion cards\nwith counts;
  
  |User|
  :Click emotion (e.g., "Happy");
  
  |System|
  :Filter images where\nemotion = 'happy';
  
  :Display filtered results;

fork again
  -> View Faces;
  :Click "Faces" in sidebar;
  
  |System|
  :Navigate to FacesPage;
  
  :Load faces from\nFaceDatabase;
  
  partition "Face Grouping" {
    repeat :For each face;
      
      :Get face_id;
      
      :Get person name;
      
      :Count associated images;
      
      :Generate face card;
      
    repeat while (More faces?) is (Yes)
    ->No;
  }
  
  :Display face grid;
  
  |User|
  :Click face card;
  
  |System|
  :Get all images with\nmatching face_id;
  
  :Display person's photos;

fork again
  -> Filter Favorites;
  :Click "Favorites" in sidebar;
  
  |System|
  :Navigate to FavoritesPage;
  
  :Filter images where\nisFavorite = true;
  
  :Display favorite images;
end fork

|User|
if (Results satisfactory?) then (Yes)
  :Browse filtered images;
  
  if (Want to view image?) then (Yes)
    :Click image;
    
    |System|
    :Open PhotoViewer;
    
    :Display full-screen image;
    
    :Show metadata panel;
  endif
else (No)
  :Modify search/filters;
  
  backward :Repeat search;
endif

if (Want to clear filters?) then (Yes)
  :Click "Clear All" or "X" button;
  
  |System|
  :Reset selectedTags = [];
  
  :Reset searchQuery = "";
  
  :Display all images;
else (No)
  :Continue browsing;
endif

stop

note right of "Text Matching"
  **Search Scope**
  • Captions (AI-generated)
  • Filenames
  • Tags
  • Detected objects
  • Scene descriptions
  
  **Case-insensitive matching**
end note

note right of "Tag Filtering"
  **Tag Logic**
  • AND: Image must have ALL tags
  • OR: Not currently supported
  • Multi-select enabled
  • Visual chips for selected tags
end note

note right of "Smart Album Generation"
  **Album Categories**
  1. Documents (screenshots)
  2. Selfies (single person)
  3. Events (gatherings)
  4. Locations (landscapes)
  5. Others (general)
  
  **AI-determined during scan**
end note

note right of "Emotion Aggregation"
  **Supported Emotions**
  • Happy, Sad, Angry
  • Surprised, Fearful
  • Disgusted, Neutral
  • Excited, Peaceful
  • Loving, Contemplative
  
  **Detected by Qwen2-VL**
end note

@enduml
